    "our_story_banner_cEnGDa": {
      "type": "our-story-banner",
      "name": "Our Story Banner",
      "settings": {
        "banner_image": "shopify://shop_images/Picture4.jpg",
        "heading": "Our Story: “It’s Care”",
        "content": "<h4>Raising the Standard in Pet Nutrition, Wellness & Happiness</h4><p>At Pawcredible, pets aren’t just animals, they’re family. They bring joy, comfort, and unconditional love every single day, and we believe they deserve the same in return.</p><p> That’s why we set out on a mission: to create the cleanest, safest, and most nutritious food possible. Food that supports your pet’s health, energy, and happiness, so they can thrive, not just survive.</p><p> Every meal we craft is made with care, using only wholesome, responsibly sourced ingredients, designed to fuel wagging tails, playful energy, and long, happy lives. Because when it comes to our pets, nothing less will do.<br/><br/></p>"
      }
    },
    "story_section1_HVRyRK": {
      "type": "story-section1",
      "name": "Story Section1",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "We believe your pets deserve the highest quality food, made with ingredients they love, sourced responsibly, supporting ethical farmers, and protecting the planet."
      }
    },
    "story_section2_LhG44Y": {
      "type": "story-section2",
      "name": "Story Section2",
      "settings": {
        "banner_image": "shopify://shop_images/Picture5_90a8166b-7d88-4cbc-b694-ede7c58f96af.jpg",
        "heading": "health, happiness, and longevity",
        "content": "<p>Hi, I’m Rob Ellery, CEO and Founder of Pawcredible.</p><p>As a lifelong dog owner, having Labradors from puppies, to rescue dogs, senior large dogs as well as chihuahuas and other small breeds, we wanted our food to encompass, all dog breeds, all sizes to ensure their health, wellness and vitality for years to come. I have spent years researching animal nutrition because I’ve always believed one simple truth: what you feed your dog shapes their health, happiness, and how long they’re by your side. Great nutrition builds strong, healthy cells - and healthy cells build a vibrant, happy pet.</p><p>That’s why at Pawcredible, we’re on a mission to make pet food as pure, safe, and nutritious as it should be. Our unique process is how we hold ourselves accountable - a step-by-step commitment to quality, taste, and integrity in every single bite.</p><p> Here’s what makes Pawcredible different:</p><ul><li><strong>Ethically sourced ingredients</strong> from trusted farms across the UK, always free from contamination.</li><li><strong>Freeze-dried to lock in real nutrition and flavor</strong> your dog craves.</li><li><strong>Zero fillers or nasties</strong> - Only essential vitamins, minerals, and natural extracts, nothing unnecessary.</li><li><strong>Every batch tested</strong> for purity, safety, and nutritional value.</li></ul><p>The result? Carefully crafted, species-appropriate recipes that support your dog’s health, fuel their energy, and help them thrive every day.</p>"
      }
    },
