    "our_story_section4_hYVXMc": {
      "type": "our-story-section4",
      "name": "Story Section4",
      "settings": {
        "banner_image": "shopify://shop_images/Picture1_f520e2df-dbab-4abf-9e75-d4c880236758.jpg",
        "heading": "Our Pawcredible Promise",
        "content": "<p><strong>1. CLEAN:</strong> Your dog deserves food that’s as real as the bond you share. That’s why up to 80% of their nutrition should come from clean, natural, species-appropriate ingredients, just like those in our freeze-dried, raw, and kibble meals. We focus on wholesome daily nutrition that fuels lifelong health, not artificial fillers or gimmicks.</p><p><strong>2. CAUSE:</strong> We care about more than what’s in the bowl. Starting with sustainable ingredients, every step of our process reflects purpose. We’re proud to support animal welfare, environmental sustainability, and initiatives that give back to the pet community</p><p><strong>3. CONNECTION:</strong> Every meal is a moment of love. Feeding time is how we connect, showing care, trust, and joy with every bite. Our mission is to make that moment special, every single day, through food your dog truly loves.</p><p><strong>4. KINDNESS:</strong> At Pawcredible, kindness guides everything we do, to pets, people, and the planet. We stand for integrity, transparency, and compassion in every bowl we make, because doing good should always taste this great.</p>",
        "button_link": "#",
        "button_text": "Learn More"
      }
    },
